  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>, java.util.Collection<java.lang.Integer>, java.util.List<java.lang.Integer>, IntCollection, PrimitiveCollection<java.lang.Integer>, IntIterable, IntList, PrimitiveList<java.lang.Integer>, PrimitiveCollectable<java.lang.Integer>

    public final class ImmutableArrayIntList
extends AbstractIntList
    Immutable array-based implementation of IntList for primitive int elements.

    This class implements List allowing seamless integration with other APIs.

    Add, Remove, Set and Clear are not supported as this class is immutable.

    Since:
    1.0
